@startuml
title Sequences - Dashboard, statistiques et rapport PDF

scale max 1050 width
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam pageMargin 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 9
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 10
actor "Utilisateur authentifie" as User
participant "DashboardPage" as Page
participant "API Laravel" as API
participant "Middleware Sanctum" as Sanctum
participant "DashboardController" as Ctrl
participant "Route report PDF" as ReportRoute
participant "DomPDF" as PDF
participant "Vue report.blade.php" as View
database "Base de donnees" as DB
participant "Navigateur" as Browser

== Chargement dashboard ==
User -> Page : Ouvrir /dashboard
Page -> API : GET /api/dashboard?days={periode}
Page -> API : GET /api/stats?days={periode}

API -> Sanctum : verifier token
Sanctum -> DB : SELECT personal_access_tokens
DB --> Sanctum : token valide

API -> Ctrl : index(request)
Ctrl -> Ctrl : getDays(request)
Ctrl -> DB : SELECT ventes avec details.medicament et user
Ctrl -> DB : SELECT medicaments WHERE quantite < 5
DB --> Ctrl : donnees
Ctrl --> API : totalRevenue totalVentes lowStock ventes
API --> Page : JSON dashboard

API -> Ctrl : stats(request)
Ctrl -> Ctrl : getDays(request)
Ctrl -> DB : SELECT ventes
Ctrl -> DB : SELECT medicaments nom quantite
DB --> Ctrl : donnees stats
Ctrl --> API : ventes par date et stocks
API --> Page : JSON stats

Page --> User : Afficher cartes, graphiques et dernieres ventes

== Changement de periode ==
User -> Page : Choisir 7j, 14j, 30j ou all
Page -> API : GET /api/dashboard?days={periode}
Page -> API : GET /api/stats?days={periode}
API --> Page : donnees filtrees
Page --> User : Rafraichir affichage

== Rapport PDF ==
User -> Page : Cliquer Telecharger PDF
Page -> API : GET /api/report/pdf?days={periode}
API -> Sanctum : verifier token
API -> ReportRoute : preparer rapport
ReportRoute -> DB : SELECT SUM ventes.total
ReportRoute -> DB : SELECT COUNT ventes
ReportRoute -> DB : SELECT medicaments WHERE quantite < 5
DB --> ReportRoute : indicateurs
ReportRoute -> PDF : loadView report donnees
PDF -> View : rendre HTML
View --> PDF : HTML
PDF --> ReportRoute : fichier PDF
ReportRoute --> API : download report.pdf
API --> Page : blob PDF
Page -> Browser : creer URL temporaire
Browser --> User : Telecharger report.pdf

@enduml
